{"tid":1196563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人你地肯醒覺未","createTime":"2019-06-09T20:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T21:55:05.000Z","uid":62802,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a546635bdccbd440f7c1065adc0102ff18328236","tid":1196563,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:59:50.000Z","msg":"今日103萬人出嚟係為咩？<br />\n為左比103萬人出嚟打卡呃like定表達訴求定要佢取消惡法？淋奠落台咪一樣下個上嚟修定惡法<br />\n可唔可以認清楚你地嘅目標<br />\n人地未回應你地就散水，一散水當無事發生繼續二讀，你地又唔出番嚟，咁朝早出嚟為咩<br />\n你地有你地遊行，佢有佢修定<br />\n你地有人唔衝擊，我可以理解，每個人都有自己嘅包袱，但係繼續和理非非真係有用咩，你地至小個人出現，撐下場面，都好過我地得幾百個，千幾個(?)禁容易比人點相<br />\n香港人自己反省下點解你地無留低，無出嚟，點解今日會白行"},{"pid":"7e8eb0d128e8a1f4608ca8dc394b40fe26a2d76d","tid":1196563,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f52322399b69d683dc387e05a9c2f7b3c41c6d01","tid":1196563,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:01:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f56b5caff86e4c5a245c78ebfbb9b332b2175e83","tid":1196563,"uid":62802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3ca212416575360b22e30f1b6a6940970ec0618","tid":1196563,"uid":122001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:02:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66d35dddeb71a9f6a9f01203bf64094b7cc0f145","tid":1196563,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:02:58.000Z","msg":"時機係咪錯咗，如果4點鐘開始做嘢會唔會更好？"},{"pid":"d2a7e70263a2de1294f784671f7cb3bd9448ead6","tid":1196563,"uid":102603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66d35dddeb71a9f6a9f01203bf64094b7cc0f145","tid":1196563,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:02:58.000Z","msg":"時機係咪錯咗，如果4點鐘開始做嘢會唔會更好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:03:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得7點"},{"pid":"287f4564a2c3595e8f7ecc59b4ff24ab9940a74c","tid":1196563,"uid":194177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"